description: Number of partitions satisfying cn(0,5) + cn(1,5) <= cn(2,5) and cn(0,5) + cn(1,5) <= cn(3,5) and cn(0,5) + cn(4,5) <= cn(2,5) and cn(0,5) + cn(4,5) <= cn(3,5).
comments: For a given partition cn(i,n) means the number of its parts equal to i modulo n.Short: 0 + 1 <= 2 and 0 + 1 <= 3 and 0 + 4 <= 2 and 0 + 4 <= 3 (ZAABB).
